						               													<description>The 24 Ore di Paperopoli is a board game for 2 to 6 players: you will be driving one of the cars of the most famous characters of Paperopoli (DuckBurg) and you will have to compete to finish the race before your opponents. During the game you will have to use the cards at your disposal, choosing every turn two among the three at your disposal, to move and maneuver, overcoming the difficulties of the path and the opponents. All players have the same cards but how to use them and when to use your superpowers will make a difference.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every card has a numeric value and a maneuver; one of the cards played use the numeric value and the other one the maneuver. Which cards to play and how to use? Everytime you play two cards with the same number you can activate a superpower but it has to be readied in the turns before using the Power maneuver.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Difficult terrain, disks and slipstream overtaking add strategic elements to the game that must be taken into account in order to win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
